clustermesh-apiserver completion 
 Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell 
 Synopsis 
 Generate the autocompletion script for clustermesh-apiserver for the specified shell.
See each sub-command's help for details on how to use the generated script. 
 Options 
   -h, --help   help for completion
 
 SEE ALSO 
 
 clustermesh-apiserver 	 - Run the ClusterMesh apiserver 
 clustermesh-apiserver completion bash 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for bash 
 clustermesh-apiserver completion fish 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for fish 
 clustermesh-apiserver completion powershell 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for powershell 
 clustermesh-apiserver completion zsh 	 - Generate the autocompletion script for zsh
